org.hps.record.triggerbank

Class TIData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.triggerbank.AbstractIntData
      • org.hps.record.triggerbank.TIData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericObject

    public class TIData
extends AbstractIntData
    Class TIData is an implementation of abstract class AbstractIntData that represents a TI trigger bit bank.
